- Patient 0 can be assigned to treatment room 0, treatment room 2, treatment room 4, or treatment room 5;
- Patient 1 can be assigned to treatment room 2 or treatment room 6;
- Patient 2 can be assigned to treatment room 0, treatment room 2, or treatment room 3;
